{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_12_level_main_12-03_end","storyGroup":"main_12","storySort":122,"storyDependence":"main_12_level_main_12-03_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"12-4","storyName":"团结就是奢望","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"费斯特等人组织自救军撤离。同时，虽然罗德岛对于“灰礼帽”并不完全信任，但也只能与他合作。变形者集群向戈尔丁展现了残酷的真相。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_12-03_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_12-03","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["洛洛","费斯特","洛克十八","伦蒂尼姆工人","伊内丝","“灰礼帽”","推进之王","阿米娅","戈尔丁","莱托中校","“茉莉”","变形者集群"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"32_g4_ordnancefactory","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"这几座军工厂......都已经空了。","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我们搬走了两条流水线，剩下的都毁了。","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"当时情况紧急，我们不知道萨卡兹雇佣兵多久会发现军工厂的动静，否则工人们能拆走更多设备的。","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"海布里区——新工业区的感觉和我在的旧工业区感觉确实不太一样，这里......","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"在萨迪恩区，我们像是扳手，敲敲打打，想办法拼凑出一切。而这里......这些传送带......我不知道，或许你们更像是齿轮。","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"稳定运转，昼夜不停。","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我们已经习惯了，人的适应力就是那么惊人。","id":16},{"type":"Dialog","id":17},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1","duration":"0.7","id":19},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","duration":"0.7","id":20},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"找到了，在这里。","id":23,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"这些集装箱上刻着符号？这是？","id":25,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我们车间流传的暗语，是当年大家约着偷懒的时候用的，没想到现在派上了用场。","id":27,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"看来想尽办法喘口气这一点，倒是哪个区的工人都一样。","id":29,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我看看，帕特他们聚拢了大部分其他区被打散的自救军成员。","id":31,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"海布里区的安全屋虽然也被袭击了，但是地块更深处的几条被当做休息站的管道还没有被发现。","id":32,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"他们应该就在那里。","id":33,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":34},{"type":"charslot","id":35},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_drone","volume":"1","id":36},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":37},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"我回来了~","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"附近萨卡兹岗哨的位置已经标记出来了。他们的人不多，看来城里的兵力要不然上了前线，要不然就追着其他人去了。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"......可露希尔小姐，我还是不觉得在无人机上搭载你的语音库是个好主意。","id":43,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"你们这架无人机的升级我可也是帮了忙的！","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"好了，不说废话了。刚才阿斯卡纶来了消息，我们的部分通讯系统有可能被维多利亚的哪个大公爵入侵了。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"我是不相信他们能入侵到底层啦，但是以防万一，我需要再做一遍全面检查。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"费斯特，会合地点的位置确认了吗？","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"已经确认了。","id":50,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"很好，我瞧瞧......","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"我们虽然有闪灵这个超级保镖，但她还需要照顾伤员们。所以，避免一切战斗，明白了吗？","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"了解。","id":55,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛克十八","text":"你们先去和剩下的自救军接触，我和克洛维希娅马上开始组织转移——","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_424_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":58},{"type":"charslot","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"走吧，洛洛。","id":62,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"啊？嗯。","id":64,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"怎么了？","id":66,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"不，没什么......","id":68,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"只是，我在想，海布里区平时有这么安静吗？","id":70,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"空气中的温度......附近甚至没有锻炉在工作。","id":72,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"这不是个好兆头，我们得加快行动。","id":74,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":75},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"charslot","id":78},{"type":"Background","image":"32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":80},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"从这里的检修管道，应该就能进入深层的......","id":84,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":85},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":87},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","channel":"w","loop":"true","id":88},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"w","fadetime":"0.8","id":89},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_unsheathe","volume":"1","id":92},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"20","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"谁！","id":94,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":95},{"type":"charslot","id":96},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":97},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":98},{"type":"Delay","time":"2.5","id":99},{"type":"charslot","id":100},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"费斯特，是我！","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"汤米！你来了！","id":106,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"你应该在下面等我们，萨卡兹的军队刚清剿过安全屋，上面可能还有巡逻的小队。","id":108,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"我......我知道，我们的损失不算轻，戴的胳膊断了，凯瑟琳给他做了下应急处理。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"你们剩下的人还有多久才到？","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"他们应该已经出发了，放心，随队的有专业医生，她会接好戴的胳膊的。","id":113,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"好，好的。","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"我们的人都聚在K13检修通道的下层。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"听说......自救军要撤出伦蒂尼姆？","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......","id":119,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"只是暂时的。","id":121,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我们还会回来，汤米，我们是伦蒂尼姆市民自救军。","id":122,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"只是，伤员们需要一个安全的地方，而伦蒂尼姆城内......无处落脚。","id":124,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"......我知道了。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"快点下去吧，凯瑟琳嘴上不说，但我们都看得出来，她很担心你。","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"你听说诺伯特区的事情了吗？天哪，那个地块被萨卡兹直接扔出城了！","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"听说，那个会飞的要塞还摧毁了大公爵们的高速军舰......那可是一艘高速军舰！","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"战争爆发了，费斯特，可我从没真正经历过......","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"我之前还以为，加入自救军不过是和以前一样，站在传送带前拧螺丝。只不过这次武器是交付给你们的而已。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"我们......这里是我们的家。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"当然，伦蒂尼姆是我们的家。","id":134,"figure":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伦蒂尼姆工人","text":"我们只属于这里，对吧。","id":136,"figure":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":137},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":138},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":139},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"charslot","id":141},{"type":"Background","image":"32_g11_victoriaroom_n","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":143},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"$ponder_loop","volume":"0.6","id":144,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......我想，我已经表现出足够的诚意了。","id":148,"figure":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"不算出人意料，我们也早就注意到了萨卡兹的秘密交通网。","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"但确实有一些值得确认的细节，我们会针对这些地方进行进一步的调查。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"其中的一些节点......我能猜到背后是谁。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"有关后续调查的结果，希望我们也能共享。","id":154,"figure":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"当然，就和我之前承诺的一样。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"罗德岛的反应很快，你们的终端信号已经重新加密了。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"如果有机会，我倒真的很想认识一下那位可露希尔工程师。","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"她一定不喜欢你。","id":160,"figure":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"贵司真是一家人才济济的制药企业。","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":164,"figure":"avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":165},{"type":"charslot","id":166},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"不过，公爵阁下从来不介意自己多一些朋友，少一些敌人。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"更何况，公爵阁下毕竟是亚历山德莉娜的血亲，她十分愿意爱护自己的这位晚辈。","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"那么，务必替我感谢她的关照。","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"殿下，我出于尊敬仍愿意这么称呼你，但这并不代表我的任何立场。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"你可以选择叫我推进之王。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"维多利亚是一副沉重的担子，亚历山德莉娜殿下，它远不如表面那般光鲜。","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"某个人——无论她是谁，自称什么，某个人的归来对这个国家毫无裨益。","id":179,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"在某些特定的情况下，如果那个人不恰当地运用了她的身份和影响力，甚至可能有害。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"这是我个人的见解。","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"那就藏好你个人的见解。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"你知道，我如今愿意暂且和你和平相处，不是因为想听你那些陈词滥调。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"殿下，我们之间没必要这么针锋相对，我不过是个听命办事的，在职权范围内我也已经表达了我的善意。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"或许是你表达得太隐晦了，要不就是我们对善意的定义有所不同。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"提出让各位前往诺伯特区不算吗？你在那里应该有位被困的朋友。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"我以为，你能感受到——我很愿意站在你的立场上推进我们的合作，我在送你人情。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#5$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"我的目标是拿到结构图，其余的行动可以由各位自行定夺，包括救援你的那位朋友。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"若你愿意直接用你手上的那把剑交换，我甚至可以考虑不辞辛劳，亲自帮忙。","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"收起你的那份恶心的假仁假义。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"听好了，我不想琢磨你和你背后的公爵在打什么主意，又在算计什么事情。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"滚远点，别挡我的路。","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"并且给我牢牢记住，阿勒黛的账，我和你，和你的主子还有得算。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我说到做到。","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_407_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"当然。","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"我刚刚收到联络，公爵阁下的特别反应小组已经为各位做好了撤离伦蒂尼姆并登上诺伯特区的准备。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"各位，出发吧。","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":208},{"type":"charslot","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1","focus":"m","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"“灰礼帽”先生，在我第一次见到你的时候，在我了解到公爵阁下对罗德岛的信息掌握到如此程度的时候，我就在想......","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"其实，你们一直都做得到，对吗？","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"你指什么？","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1","focus":"m","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"无论是我们，还是萨卡兹，乃至自救军的行动，你们从来不是一无所知。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"也并不像各位想象的那般简单，那般完整。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"萨卡兹，特别是王庭中的某些人就算对我们来说也很棘手，我有很多同事因此丧命。","id":219,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1","focus":"m","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可你们自始至终都牢牢把握着事情的走向。","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#19$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你们......尤其是你们背后那些维多利亚的大公爵们，为什么要放任事态发展到这种地步？","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"那位卡兹戴尔的摄政王是个了不起的对手，我想，这一点连老威灵顿都会承认。卡兹戴尔军事委员会的那些技术与装备也让人印象深刻。","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这种夸赞由一位维多利亚大公爵意志的代行者说出，未免也太像句讽刺了。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"据我们的分析，特雷西斯的实力确实很强大，但是远不该让维多利亚陷入如此被动的境地。","id":228,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#20$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"现在我明白了，你们只是选择袖手旁观。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#20$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你们眼睁睁看着自己的国家陷入战火。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#20$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"阿米娅，罗德岛的小小领导人，你多大？十五岁还是十六岁？你甚至还只是个孩子。","id":233,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"你们痛恨鲜血，你们痛恨战争。但我要说明一点，我们也没那么喜欢这些东西。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"但对于我们，战争的目的永远不是它本身，战争是政治的延伸，萨卡兹们需要用一场战争团结自己，维多利亚未必不需要。","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"只不过，团结在谁的周围值得探讨。","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#20$1","focus":"m","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"仅仅为了这一点，你们就——","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#20$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"这一点很重要，比你想的重要得多。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"战争是残酷的，它会带来伤害，带来死亡，它会让我们以最赤裸裸的样子暴露在彼此面前，它会扯下所有伪装。","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"在历史行进的某些阶段，我们需要这种坦诚。每个人都需要。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"做好准备吧，罗德岛的各位，我们该启程了。","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":244},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":245},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"charslot","id":248},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_offce","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":250},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.6","id":251,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":252},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":253},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"n","loop":"false","id":254},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"n","fadetime":"1.5","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","duration":"1","id":256},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"茉莉！你也被他们抓来了？！","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"莱托，她只是个普通的老师，学校里的孩子仍需要人照顾。","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你已经摧毁了你想摧毁的，你还想牵连多少人？","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_649_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"您来了，阁下。","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_649_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"女妖又找上我们了，找上了我们其中之一。","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我这就命令部队前去支援。","id":268,"figure":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"不用，与他散散步也不错。","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"去找老红眼病吧，他正开了瓶好酒等着你，我们已经厌烦听他唠叨那些陈年旧事了。","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"你是个比我们更好的听众。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_649_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"——我明白了，那么容我告退。","id":274,"figure":"avg_npc_649_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":275},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":276},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_649_1#9$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":277},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":278},{"type":"charslot","id":279},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":280},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你......","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"none","id":283},{"type":"Text","text":"戈尔丁从没感觉到自己的喉咙如此干涩。眼前的人与她记忆中的茉莉别无二致，连最细微的小动作都一模一样。","id":284},{"type":"Text","text":"她总微微皱起眉头，关注着顽皮孩子们的一举一动，她会在晚餐时分端上面包，轻轻斥责没有洗手的人。","id":285},{"type":"Text","text":"她仍是那副表情，可为什么......","id":286},{"type":"Text","text":"戈尔丁后背的汗水浸透了衣裳。","id":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"兰西的拇指昨天又擦伤了，放心，我给他涂好药啦。","id":289,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"他总是这么让人操心。","id":290,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你是......什么......","id":292,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"那位老师已经回到了学校，她能照看好那些孩子的。","id":294,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"聊聊天怎么样？","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"放松点，不过是场闲谈，如果你还是感到不舒服，我们也可以继续用这张脸主人的身份与您相处，戈尔丁女士。","id":297,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"也许先聊聊天气啦，聊聊孩子们的学业？还有那场戏，戈尔丁女士，现在想起来我都忍不住要掉泪。","id":298,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"一眨眼，孩子们都长得这么大了。","id":299,"figure":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":300},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"够了，别再用茉莉的语气和我说话！别再顶着那张脸！你这怪物！","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你到底......想干什么？","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"all","id":305},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":306},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":307},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":308},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_humanchange","id":309},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"要喝茶吗？莱托的品味不错，他这里的茶叶相当美味。","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......","id":315,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"特雷西斯委派的那些任务也算有个交代啦，接下来，我们可以稍微休息一下。","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......你在我身边多久了？","id":319,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"没你想象的那么久，不过，我们能不能跳过那些无聊的工作话题？","id":321,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"现在是休息时间，我们想做点自己真正感兴趣的事。","id":322,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"比如——","id":323,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"听一听你对这个时代的想法，听一听你对这一切的结论。","id":325,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......我不明白。","id":327,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你......你们借助我毁了自救军，我对你们已经没有利用价值了。","id":329,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我......该死！我亲手交出了这一切......","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"别这么自责，戈尔丁，这没什么大不了的，我们有千万种办法拿到自救军据点的位置，你不是唯一的情报源。","id":332,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"这也许有点伤人，你甚至不是称得上重要的一个。","id":333,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"但我们对你这个人确实有些小小的兴趣，我们很享受看你的那些作品，以及和你本人聊天。","id":334,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"所以，陪我们聊聊吧，这没什么深意，只是闲谈。","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"这样的闲谈我们已经发起过无数次，用无数的身份，与无数的人进行过。","id":337,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"可我们依然很困惑，我们还是不愿放弃任何一次可能得出答案的机会。","id":338,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"戈尔丁女士，你觉得——","id":340,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"我们应该如何生活？","id":341,"figure":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":342},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":344},{"type":"charslot","id":345},{"type":"Image","id":346}],"characters":["洛洛","费斯特","洛克十八","伦蒂尼姆工人","伊内丝","“灰礼帽”","推进之王","阿米娅","戈尔丁","莱托中校","“茉莉”","变形者集群"]}